OL,3,CEni Aluko says Joey Barton 'absolutely
OL,4,Cintended' to cause harm with posts
OL,6,FFootball pundit Eni Aluko has said
OL,7,FJoey Barton "thrives on hurting
OL,8,Fpeople" and intended to cause harm
OL,9,Fthrough his grossly offensive social
OL,10,Fmedia posts.
OL,12,FThe ex-footballer was sentenced on
OL,13,FMonday to six months in custody
OL,14,Fsuspended for 18 months, for making
OL,15,Fthe posts about Ms Aluko, fellow
OL,16,Fpundit Lucy Ward, and broadcaster
OL,17,FJeremy Vine.
OL,19,FSpeaking to the BBC's Newsnight
OL,20,Fprogramme on Monday, Ms Aluko said the
OL,21,Fsentence sent "a huge message".
